snippet.title: Super Smash Bros New Challenger King K. Rool (Mii DLC WII U Smash Bros 4) All HD
snippet.description:
King K. Rool enters the battle! Super Smash Bros. received a fresh update that added balance changes, a new Mii Fighter costume, and more for free

Super Smash Bros. 4's latest DLC is very centered around Mii Fighter costumes. Aside from the two clic stages now available for purchase, most of the latest content comes in the form of Mii Fighter outfits. Chrom, Black Knight, Lloyd Irving, King K Rool, Samus, Zero Suit Samus enters the fight / battle!
